title: 075 - Off The Rails
description: Today's show goes completely off the rails as the guys cover a full Pod FOD. They cover a variety of subjects, but this thing gets derailed pretty quickly and they just start letting it rip and having a good time. It's a pretty fun one. Come and laugh with us, enjoy.
